      <title>摩根大通将利用 ETF 策略吸引加拿大散户投资者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/jpmorgan-set-to-woo-canadian-retail-investors-with-etf-strategy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通公司计划通过推出新的交易所交易基金和在边境以北开展招聘活动，占据加拿大散户投资市场的很大一部分份额。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/jpmorgan-set-to-woo-canadian-retail-investors-with-etf-strategy</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 18:22:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿拉斯加航空出售债券和贷款以再融资夏威夷债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/alaska-air-selling-bonds-loan-to-refinance-hawaiian-borrowings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿拉斯加航空集团公司 (Alaska Air Group Inc.) 正在出售约 12.5 亿美元的美国高等级债券以及以其飞行常客计划担保的贷款，以为其收购夏威夷航空公司 (Hawaiian Holdings Inc.) 相关的债务进行再融资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/alaska-air-selling-bonds-loan-to-refinance-hawaiian-borrowings</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 16:45:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>二叠纪天然气开始通过德克萨斯州马特洪管道输送</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/permian-gas-starts-flowing-via-matterhorn-pipeline-in-texas</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马特洪峰快线管道 (Matterhorn Express Pipeline) 已开始向 Williams Cos. 的 Transco 管道输送天然气，这是二叠纪盆地中游基础设施期待已久的补充。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/permian-gas-starts-flowing-via-matterhorn-pipeline-in-texas</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 13:31:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波音公司考虑通过出售股票筹集至少 100 亿美元资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/boeing-said-to-weigh-raising-at-least-10-billion-selling-stock</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，波音公司正考虑通过发行新股筹集至少 100 亿美元，以补充因持续罢工而进一步消耗的现金储备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/boeing-said-to-weigh-raising-at-least-10-billion-selling-stock</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 10:08:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗向以色列发射火箭弹 油价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-1</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗向以色列发射火箭弹后，油价飙升，加大了该地区原油供应中断的风险。该地区原油产量占全球原油产量的三分之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-1</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 23:26:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
